            distributed, sequentially consistent file system in C++ (gRPC,
            multithreading) and ran RL experiments (exact algorithms vs.
            approximate algorithms). Current focus: mechanistic
            interpretability, robustness & evaluation, and reproducible ML.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

